{"id":611864,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rian_Johnson","text":"Rian Craig Johnson (born December 17, 1973) is an American movie director, screenwriter, editor and actor. He is best known for directing the movies \"Brick\" (2005), \"The Brothers Bloom\" (2008), \"Looper\" (2012), ' (2017) and \"Knives Out\" (2019). He has directed three episodes of the AMC series \"Breaking Bad\". He has also had small roles in ' (2016) and \"BoJack Horseman\".\nJohnson was born in Silver Spring, Maryland. He has been dating movie writer Karina Longworth since 2011.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":50},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"movie director","offset":59},{"uri":"Screenwriter","surface_form":"screenwriter","offset":75},{"uri":"Editor","surface_form":"editor","offset":89},{"uri":"Actor","surface_form":"actor","offset":100},{"uri":"Movie","surface_form":"movie","offset":142},{"uri":"Brick_(movie)","surface_form":"Brick","offset":150},{"uri":"The_Brothers_Bloom","surface_form":"The Brothers Bloom","offset":166},{"uri":"Looper_(movie)","surface_form":"Looper","offset":195},{"uri":"Knives_Out_(movie)","surface_form":"Knives Out","offset":225},{"uri":"Episode","surface_form":"episode","offset":267},{"uri":"AMC_(TV_channel)","surface_form":"AMC","offset":283},{"uri":"Breaking_Bad","surface_form":"Breaking Bad","offset":295},{"uri":"BoJack_Horseman","surface_form":"BoJack Horseman","offset":355},{"uri":"Silver_Spring%2C_Maryland","surface_form":"Silver Spring","offset":393},{"uri":"Maryland","surface_form":"Maryland","offset":408},{"uri":"Dating","surface_form":"dating","offset":430},{"uri":"Karina_Longworth","surface_form":"Karina Longworth","offset":450}]}